metadata.name: Visible Frogs #1
metadata.description: Feeling flush with crypto, This amazing Frog and his thousands of rare hommies decided to treat themselves to a fancy dinner at an exclusive restaurant. They laughed and joked and toasted to their newfound wealth, all the while marveling at the wonders of the blockchain. As they walked home, full and happy, He couldn't help but feel grateful for his amazing friends and the amazing world they lived in. Who would have thought that a bunch of frogs could be so tech-savvy? It just goes to show that anything is possible with a little bit of memes, curiosity and a lot of determination.
